annotationDatas.title: Trochlear Notch
annotationDatas.content: The point of articulation with the trochlea of the humerus.

annotationDatas.title: Radial Notch
annotationDatas.content: Point of articulation with the proximal radius.

annotationDatas.title: Olecranon
annotationDatas.content: Insertion point of the triceps brachii.

annotationDatas.title: Nutrient Foramen
annotationDatas.content: A tunnel through the cortex of the bone. Creates an entrance for a nutrient artery to supply the bone.

annotationDatas.title: Styloid Process of the Ulna
annotationDatas.content: Origin of the ulnar collateral ligament.
